data.title: Buppy Dog Island Sketch Pack by vaguecreature
data.meta_description: (18+) Post-TF illustrations of 10 various bimbofied and puppified villagers
data.text:
NSFW image pack of 10 exclusive illustrations not published anywhere else.

By popular demand, here's 10 new characters who've been given the buppy collar treatment, turning them into bubbly bimbo doggies! Originally this was just supposed to be sketches but I ended up having fun and colouring/shading them. (oops!)

As usual this pack is supposed to act as a sort of tip jar, but with some cool bonus images attached. Thanks for supporting me! â¤ï¸
